alloc::collections::VecDeque::<T, A>::pu.doc:
Appends an element to the back of the deque.

# Examples

```
use std::collections::VecDeque;

let mut buf = VecDeque::new();
buf.push_back(1);
buf.push_back(3);
assert_eq!(3, *buf.back().unwrap());
